data.description: Welcome Home! Come and see this beautiful Master On The Main 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath. This home has NEW lighting, NEW appliances, NEWER roof and carpet. You'll discover a bright and open interior with plenty of natural light and a neutral color palette, complimented by a fireplace. The kitchen is ready for cooking with ample counter space and cabinets for storage. Relax in your primary suite on the main floor with a walk in closet included. The master bath boasts dual sinks and separate tub/shower. Going up the 2 story foyer enter a floor with 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom. The back yard is the perfect spot to kick back with the included sitting area. Like what you hear? Come see it for yourself!
